- Volume scaling

### Integration Tests
- Actual sound playback on each platform
- Latency measurement (must be < 50ms from event to sound start)

### E2E Tests
- Full flow: rotate → hear tick
- Boundary hit → hear different sound
- Mute toggle → hear mute sound

